{"tid":841551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來飼養兔仔可令人心境平靜！🌟","createTime":"2018-09-29T15:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T08:05:42.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b1771f72b274a5556e1e049c3b021c4150eb2919","tid":841551,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:14:22.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！☺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9Vf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7bd5f364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a><br />\n<br />\n當兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)時, 這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活，因為兔子Binky是兔子最開心的狀態。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9Vf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=204c4fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em>N.B.:</em></strong></span> 實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9Vf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=dfbb6dd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"0720fb876f58682f5b1e885ee3b4c87a9f894fc1","tid":841551,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:43:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>怎樣訓練兔仔去廁所？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n訓練兔仔🐰去廁所是很簡單的。糞便是沒有臭味的，而且是乾的，所以通常可以拿上來放回兔子的廁所（牠們便會知道要去廁所大小便）然後洗手。尿有時會有少少味，最好把白醋加水放入噴霧樽，然後清洗地板，這樣的話會立刻清除味道及減少牠們在這裏小便。兔子在籠裡大便是正常的，是表示這個籠是牠的地盤。開始的時候在籠內訓練，然後逐漸地加一點兒範圍。不要一開始就讓牠在整個家周圍走，這樣會比較難訓練。<br />\n<br />\n每次兔子在籠外隨地大小便，大聲說No, 然後輕輕地帶牠回到廁所，讓牠知道是不可以的。將隨地的大便放回廁所內，以及隨地的小便用廁紙抹完放入廁所內，牠便會知道要在廁所內大小便。每次牠在廁所內大小便，就給他零食作獎勵。選擇獎勵，不要懲罰。記住不要打兔子，牠們與狗和貓不同，如果打，牠永遠不會忘記，令到與主人關係和信任差。壓力(stress) 亦可以會令兔子生病。兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(predatory animals)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。他們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會驚嚇兔子。當牠們受驚時，groom(撫摸和親吻)牠們是很重要，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。<br />\n<br />\n當然，兔子要絕育才可以訓練去廁所，因為霸地盤(territorial marker), 絕育後會大大減少霸地盤。另外，兔子是很容易患上生殖器疾病的動物，所以絕育也會令牠們更健康和長命！<br />\n<br />\n當然，有時候牠們不開心不聽話或者少少霸地盤原因也會隨地大便。<br />\n以下3個videos 有教, 步驟簡單:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsB7SILsOns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzsB7SILsOns&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9Vf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=07934067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsB7SILsOns</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gP4IaOQsKl4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgP4IaOQsKl4&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9Vf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3cadd4bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gP4IaOQsKl4</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GHRkf5z6EQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0GHRkf5z6EQ&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9Vf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=78af1068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GHRkf5z6EQ</a>"},{"pid":"8a23396843867d0f2ef1d6eb33bb5fa3ad345ebf","tid":841551,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a12d47fa6ff0625e91740c6998ae99296527a45","tid":841551,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a23396843867d0f2ef1d6eb33bb5fa3ad345ebf","tid":841551,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:16:45.000Z","msg":"Rabbits are prey animals"},{"pid":"6e2b760f43fe2c0ac91353bba231038e31094f93","tid":841551,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:02:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0j8Gt5JQPKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0j8Gt5JQPKc&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9Vf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8557b7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0j8Gt5JQPKc</a>"},{"pid":"1c04cb8a055f2449ed9491056e401b2ab8b6a8ad","tid":841551,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T08:05:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主人走到哪裡, 這隻兔子就永遠跟著走到哪裡。還有, 原來兔子懂得微笑, 以下video可看到：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihSd1mss3bA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DihSd1mss3bA&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9Vf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f0a98c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihSd1mss3bA</a>"}]}